thumb.title: TETORIS テトリス - 【斉木ロイド UTAU】
thumb.description: "saikiloid" is a saiki kusuo jinriki UTAU, made by me (with love) using the audio files from Saiki Kusuo no Psi Nan: Shijou Psi Dai no Psi Nan?! on 3DS♥︎ Tetoris by ‪Hiiragi Magnetite, off-vocal provided also by Hiiragi Magnetite♥︎ UST by ‪jootersblaccat♥︎ Saiki Kusuo voice talent by Hiroshi Kamiya♥︎ Zundamon UTAU ft as backing vocals♥︎ Danny Denkine ft as backing vocals♥︎ Mixing done by ‪kamimint‬♥︎ Rotating Saiki from the Saiki Kusuo no Psi Nan anime's fourth opening, Oteage Psychics♥︎ Saiki Kusuo and Saiki Kusuo no Psi Nan are the creations of Shuichi Aso♥︎ Saiki Kusuo no Psi Nan: Shijou Psi Dai no Psi Nan?! developed by Bandai Namco Studios and Natsume Atari, published by Bandai Namco Entertainment♥︎ tuning, art, editing, and "saikiloid" jinriki bank by startropicz (me)
